{"tid":1606661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解黨鐵成日都有廣播話請勿帶氫氣球進入車站範圍？","createTime":"2019-09-30T15:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:39:17.000Z","uid":256741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2767c185c8cb6c4c5c1f15ef2bc669c363d1203","tid":1606661,"uid":256741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"係唔係得黨鐵有咁嘅規例？反而去到外國又有唔多覺有。。。點解黨鐵咁驚輕氣球？有冇人知點解？<br />\n<br />\n求解答。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675cd77bdc77985f29d97a82441709e4ee9fd94c","tid":1606661,"uid":86375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:33:44.000Z","msg":"金屬氣球<br />\n因為怕氣球飛上去掂到高壓電纜,會跳制"},{"pid":"5a30a0b7438b7470fcada670d6f8c195780726c1","tid":1606661,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140203%2F00410_097.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6rM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=3035bcd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html</a><br />\n<br />\n金屬氦氣球玩具隨時變成鐵路炸彈。氦氣球會影響電纜運作，被港鐵列為違禁品，以往港鐵職員發現乘客持氦氣球進入港鐵範圍會即時沒收。但本報發現，近月港鐵職員防備鬆懈，乘客攜帶氦氣球入閘視而不見，鐵路範圍處處見到「鐵路炸彈」。專家警告，如氦氣球飄起觸到鐵路電纜，會引致電力短路，可能會引起小火，導致電力供應系統「跳掣」，引發交通大災難。"},{"pid":"2657172991614e2a2acbaad3f72a4b52244faec7","tid":1606661,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685429c0015ec3fa4d3e72cd7a230bc412307619","tid":1606661,"uid":256741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a30a0b7438b7470fcada670d6f8c195780726c1","tid":1606661,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140203%2F00410_097.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6rM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=3035bcd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html</a><br />\n<br />\n金屬氦氣球玩具隨時變成鐵路炸彈。氦氣球會影響電纜運作，被港鐵列為違禁品，以往港鐵職員發現乘客持氦氣球進入港鐵範圍會即時沒收。但本報發現，近月港鐵職員防備鬆懈，乘客攜帶氦氣球入閘視而不見，鐵路範圍處處見到「鐵路炸彈」。專家警告，如氦氣球飄起觸到鐵路電纜，會引致電力短路，可能會引起小火，導致電力供應系統「跳掣」，引發交通大災難。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖？好不安。大家叫啲小朋友千奇唔好咁做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46517196d4401f4229a650ff3e3775ddf64722d","tid":1606661,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"推"}]}